{
  "stem": "294.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were put into an old Polish fortress in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, of course, straw-- and here we coming from those very nice apartment, with plenty of food, and-- and clothes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And here we come-- straw on the floor-- cold.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was-- this was November-- the beginning of November, and it's very cold in Poland--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, '39.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as far as-- the Polish Catholics were registered by the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were received by the-- the representatives of the Jewish-- like here, Jewish Federation-- Jewish community-- force-- Jewish community center.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were supposed to register.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as we were standing in line, my mother and I-- crying and being very upset-- a young man came to that line and ask us if we have a place to stay-- if we have family or friends in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know no one-- anyone in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, don't worry, I take you to my house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have two empty apartments.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You will be with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, we stood for hours outside, already in the snow, and the cold, and not dressed very-- very well, waiting until they were finished with their registration.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then this young man came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know if you know what a dorozka is.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know what a dorozka is?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's like a coach.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a horse-drawn carriage.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, in Poland, before the war, there were very few private cars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had dorozkas.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had trolley cars.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this was our transportations.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this guy took two dorozkas, because he ask somebody else to come with him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, my mother and I, were in one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said to us that he has to stop in front of his place of work.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
